  "methods": "<p>793 fish samples were genotyped using GT-seq panel developed in this study. After filtering (SNP with &gt;50% missing data; samples with&gt;30% missing data) the final datasets were converted in <em>rubias</em> format for each of the five (5) species/region datasets used in our paper for estimating assignment accuracies for GSI studies.</p>",
